        <title>Activity: To describe and illustrate different cultures' ways of writing [LO 1.2]</title>
        <para id="id1169877036886"/>
        <list id="id1169879851413" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Can you deduce from this how the Romans would have written 11? </item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1169882924410">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id1169876040969">1.2 How would they have written 15? </para>
        <para id="id1169876537019">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id1169878995974">1.3 Where are these Roman numerals still used nowadays? </para>
        <para id="id1169880276651">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id1169879121379"/>
        <list id="id1169876427548" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Look carefully at the following:</item>
        </list>
